{"prompt": "Develop a landing page for a new mobile application. The brand should be represented by a zesty lemon yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>ZestApp - Your Fresh Start</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #FFEA00;\n            --secondary-bg-color: #F8F8F8;\n            --dark-text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --button-border-color: #FFEA00;\n            --button-hover-bg: #FFD700;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \"Apple Color Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Emoji\", \"Segoe UI Symbol\";\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 960px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            max-width: 600px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-buttons {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 20px;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n\n        .button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            min-width: 200px;\n        }\n\n        .button.primary {\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            border: 2px solid var(--button-border-color);\n        }\n\n        .button.primary:hover {\n            background-color: var(--button-hover-bg);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            border-color: var(--button-hover-bg);\n        }\n\n        .footer {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-bg-color);\n            color: var(--dark-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        .footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n\n            .cta-buttons {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n            }\n\n            .button {\n                min-width: unset;\n                width: 80%;\n            }\n\n            .hero {\n                min-height: 80vh;\n                padding: 60px 20px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>ZestApp</h1>\n            <p>Unleash Your Productivity. Freshly Designed for You.</p>\n            <p>Discover a vibrant new way to organize your life, track your goals, and stay motivated. ZestApp brings energy and simplicity to your daily routine.</p>\n            <div class=\"cta-buttons\">\n                <a href=\"#download-app-store\" class=\"button primary\">Download on App Store</a>\n                <a href=\"#download-google-play\" class=\"button primary\">Get it on Google Play</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 ZestApp. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}